In such environments, protecting sensitive information and conversations is vital. Tools that allow secure, offline communication without leaving digital traces help reduce the risk of being tracked or targeted. Key topics to explore include cross-border activism, digital surveillance, authoritarian repression, secure messaging, and offline encryption methods.